<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="37" type="habitat">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="37">Habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="37">Forest species found on vertical and fallen tree trunks, sometimes in forest floor; occasionally also outside the forest (but close to the trees).</paragraph>
